_sText:
The CT's are stranded atop a tower with only snipers to defend themselves. The ravage T's are out to destroy the steel girders that support the tower with their knives to topple it, sending the CT's into the depths of hell :O


This map is fairly dark. Actualy, very dark. The T's have pleanty of cover to hide behind. But the Girders don't have alot of health, so if the T's do enough damage than the corresponding portion of the tower will fall to. DOOM
=O *GASP*
